# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Accesses a row at an index.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(position: Int) -> DataFrame.Row { get set }
```

## Parameters

- **position**: A valid index to a row in the collection.

## Accessing Elements

- **subscript(_:)**: Returns a row collection from an index range.
